-- Spain to Review Army to Boost Savings, Morenes Tells Vanguardia
-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 2012-03-11T12:54:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-11/spain-to-review-army-to-boost-savings-morenes-tells-vanguardia.html
Spain  will review the size of its
army to make savings and reduce the budget deficit, Defense
Minister Pedro Morenes said in an interview with  La Vanguardia .  The  Defense Ministry ’s contribution to cutting the budget
deficit will be “reasonable” and similar to that of other
ministries, Morenes said, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Manuel Baigorri in Madrid at 
